<h2>Hide (Close) a Panel</h2>
<p>Hiding a panel is easy.</p>
<div class="w3-panel w3-red w3-display-container">
    <span class="w3-button w3-large w3-red w3-display-topleft" onclick="this.parentElement.style.display='none'">×</span>
    <p>Click on the X to close this panel.</p>
    <p>Click on the X to close this panel.</p>
</div>
